query_result.query:
-- TOTAL VALUE OF ORDERS WITHOUT DELIVERY FEES-NO COUPONS
select case
when orders_order.store_id=1 then 'Kallithea'
when orders_order.store_id=2 then 'Marousi'
when orders_order.store_id=3 then 'Psychiko'
when orders_order.store_id=4 then 'Argyroupoli'
end, 
count(distinct orders_order.id),
sum(orders_orderitem.price* orders_orderitem.quantity)  from orders_order
inner join orders_orderitem on orders_order.id=orders_orderitem.order_id
where orders_order.payment_status='paid'
and (orders_order.status='delivered' or orders_order.status='ready_for_delivery')
and orders_order.created_at::DATE=DATE(NOW())
and orders_orderitem.price>-2
group by orders_order.store_id
